        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Strength in Diversity Act of </b><strong>2022</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a program through which the Department of Education may award planning and implementation grants to specified educational agencies (e.g., local educational agencies) to improve diversity and reduce or eliminate racial or socioeconomic isolation in publicly funded early childhood education programs, public elementary schools, or public secondary schools.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
